# 🔄 Maono Platform — Workflow Métier API

## Vue d'ensemble Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    Client["Frontend / Mobile"] -->|HTTP Request| API["Maono.Api"]
    API -->|MediatR| Pipeline["CQRS Pipeline"]
    Pipeline -->|ICommand| Handlers["Handlers"]
    Pipeline -->|IQuery| Handlers
    Handlers -->|Repository| DB["PostgreSQL"]
    Handlers -->|S3 SDK| Minio["MinIO Storage"]
    
    subgraph "Pipeline (automatique)"
        P1["LoggingBehavior"] --> P2["ValidationBehavior"]
        P2 --> P3["TransactionBehavior (ICommand only)"]
    end
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Aucun contrôleur n'accède directement à la base de données.** Tout passe par MediatR → Pipeline → Handler → Repository.

---

## 1. 🔐 Authentification & Sessions

**Contrôleur :** `AuthController` — **Seul contrôleur partiellement public**

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as AuthController
    participant H as Handler
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>API: POST /api/auth/register
    API->>H: RegisterCommand
    H->>DB: Create IdentityUser + DomainUser
    H-->>API: { accessToken, refreshToken }
    API-->>U: 200 OK

    U->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API->>H: LoginCommand (+ device fingerprint)
    H->>DB: Validate credentials + Create DeviceSession
    H-->>API: { accessToken, refreshToken, sessionId }
    API-->>U: 200 OK

    U->>API: POST /api/auth/refresh
    API->>H: RefreshTokenCommand
    H->>DB: Rotate tokens
    H-->>API: { newAccessToken, newRefreshToken }

    U->>API: GET /api/auth/sessions 🔒
    API->>H: GetActiveSessionsQuery
    H-->>API: List<SessionDto>

    U->>API: POST /api/auth/sessions/{id}/revoke 🔒
    API->>H: RevokeSessionCommand
    H->>DB: Mark session as revoked
```

| Endpoint | Méthode | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/api/auth/register` | POST | ❌ Public | Inscription utilisateur |
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | ❌ Public | Connexion + device tracking |
| `/api/auth/refresh` | POST | ❌ Public | Rafraîchir les tokens JWT |
| `/api/auth/sessions` | GET | 🔒 Bearer | Lister les sessions actives |
| `/api/auth/sessions/{id}/revoke` | POST | 🔒 Bearer | Révoquer une session |
| `/api/auth/sessions/revoke-others` | POST | 🔒 Bearer | Révoquer toutes les autres sessions |

