## 5. 📢 Campagnes

**Contrôleur :** `CampaignsController` — 🔒 `[Authorize]`

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft : POST /api/campaigns
    Draft --> Active : PUT status=Active
    Active --> Paused : PUT status=Paused
    Paused --> Active : PUT status=Active
    Active --> Completed : PUT status=Completed
    Completed --> [*]
    Draft --> Archived : DELETE
    Active --> Archived : DELETE
```

| Endpoint | Méthode | Policy | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/api/campaigns` | POST | `CanManageContent` | Créer une campagne |
| `/api/campaigns` | GET | 🔒 Bearer | Lister (avec `?clientId=`) |
| `/api/campaigns/{id}` | GET | 🔒 Bearer | Détails + KPIs + tags |
| `/api/campaigns/{id}` | PUT | `CanManageContent` | Modifier la campagne |
| `/api/campaigns/{id}` | DELETE | `CanManageContent` | Archiver (soft-delete) |
| `/api/campaigns/{id}/kpi-targets` | PATCH | `CanManageContent` | Définir les objectifs KPI |

