## 8. ✅ Approbations (Approval Cycles)

**Contrôleur :** `ApprovalsController` — 🔒 `[Authorize]`

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant CM as Content Manager
    participant API as ApprovalsController
    participant Client as Client (via Portal)

    CM->>API: POST /api/approvals/internal
    Note right of API: SubmitInternalDecision (Approve/Reject)
    
    alt Internal Approved
        Client->>API: POST /api/portal/{token}/decisions
        Note right of API: Décision client via portail anonyme
        alt Client Approved
            API-->>CM: Content → Approved status
        else Revision Needed
            API-->>CM: New revision round starts
        end
    else Internal Rejected
        API-->>CM: Content → RevisionNeeded
    end
```

| Endpoint | Méthode | Policy | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/api/approvals/internal` | POST | `CanApprove` | Soumettre décision interne |
| `/api/approvals/client` | POST | 🔒 Bearer | Soumettre décision client |
| `/api/approvals/contents/{contentId}/cycles` | GET | 🔒 Bearer | Historique des cycles |

---

